___account_objects.description: Array of objects owned by this account. Each object is in its raw ledger format.

___limit.description: (May be omitted) The limit that was used in this request, if any.

___ledger_current_index.description: (May be omitted) The sequence number of the ledger that was used to generate this response.

___account.description: Unique address of the account this request corresponds to.

___ledger_index.description: (May be omitted) The sequence number of the ledger that was used to generate this response.

___ledger_hash.description: (May be omitted) The identifying hash of the ledger that was used to generate this response.

___validated.description: If included and set to true, the information in this request comes from a validated ledger version. Otherwise, the information is subject to change.
